newpath
x0 y0 moveto
x1 y1 lineto
stroke
grestore

  gsave
  
0 setgray
newpath
/n poly length def
poly n 1 sub get
aload pop moveto
poly {
aload pop lineto
} forall
stroke
  
  grestore

/quoly poly line hodgman-sutherland def

newpath
