P 5 get aload pop
sw hw 24 60 mkarrow 
gsave
1 0 0 setrgbcolor fill
grestore
stroke

grestore

% --- now do the replacement arrow ---

gsave
1 setlinecap
currentlinewidth 0.7 mul setlinewidth
R aload pop translate
newpath
S 0 get R 0 get sub 
S 1 get R 1 get sub 
sw hw 24 69 mkarrow
gsave
1 1 1 setrgbcolor 
fill
grestore
stroke
grestore


